source/Katarina_Waters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"her love\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 392}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 421}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"never-give-up attitude\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"her first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Liverpudlian took silver in the heptathlon on Friday inParis, coming second toBelgianrival Nafissatou Thiam.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\", \"score\": 0.9921012116706439, \"rank\": 0.007961675922259215, \"text\": \"Liverpudlian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\"}, {\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafissatou_Thiam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nafissatou Thiam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafissatou_Thiam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafissatou_Thiam\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"the heptathlon\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday inParis\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson-Thompson, 31, on Saturday spoke about her love for Liverpool and how it shaped her as a person.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 673, \"end\": 682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999361433667154, \"rank\": 6.386042054158023e-05, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Johnson-Thompson\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"her love\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love the people of Liverpool and I love what they stand for and that shapes my character, of that never-give-up attitude, and that underdog attitude and yes, it means the world She said: \\\"Liverpool is my home, it always is my home even if I train and live elsewhere.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999361433667154, \"rank\": 6.386042054158023e-05, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999361433667154, \"rank\": 6.386042054158023e-05, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"my character\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 809}, {\"ngram\": \"that never-give-up attitude\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"my home\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"my home\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love the people of Liverpool and I love what they stand for and that shapes my character, of that never-give-up attitude, and that underdog attitude and yes, it means the world.\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1012, \"end\": 1021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999361433667154, \"rank\": 6.386042054158023e-05, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1008}, {\"ngram\": \"my character\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"that never-give-up attitude\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I started my career at Liverpool Harriers and I am indebted to them as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999361433667154, \"rank\": 6.386042054158023e-05, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson-Thompson said the silver medal was \\\"a long time coming\\\".\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1316, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Johnson-Thompson\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1268}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver medal\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It feels incredible that you know we got one over the line.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a long time coming, it's been a very short cycle but it's my fourthOlympicsand I am really happy to add that medal to my collection,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"a very short cycle\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"that medal\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"my collection\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson-Thompson said: \\\"I have got absolutely no regrets.\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Johnson-Thompson\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"absolutely no regrets\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I tried my absolute best and my best on that day was second place by about 30 points, so you know I was very close to an Olympic gold medal and to me that's just validated our team's belief that it was possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1804, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that day\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"second place\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"about 30 points\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"our team's belief\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if there were times she doubted she would get there, she said: \\\"I have had doubts all the time, every athlete I feel like, even if they do not admit it, always has doubts - crippling doubts, but luckily I have got a team around me that has the belief in me that I sometimes do not have in myself, and that leads me to do great things and I am so grateful to them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1831}, {\"ngram\": \"doubts\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"doubts - crippling doubts\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2001}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"the belief\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"great things\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked about her plans for the future, she said: \\\"I feel like as long as I am competitive I will continue to do heptathlon.\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her plans\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"heptathlon\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really happy that I am able to put together my heptathlon in a different way now and it's given me such longevity in the sport.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heptathlon\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"a different way\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2384}, {\"ngram\": \"such longevity\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really really excited for the next couple of years.\\\"\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next couple\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"inPlease\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2596}, {\"ngram\": \"your browser\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2617}]}]}"